\section{Directions}
You may select a basis set by following these steps:
\begin{enumerate} 
\item Run unravel on your favorite directory of processed C files.

\item Click on the 'Run Basis Set Viewer' button. This will open The Basis Set
	   Viewer Selection Panel.

\item Select a C file.
 
\item Click on the 'Select' button.
 
\item Select a function.
 
\item Choose a basis path.
\end{enumerate}
The basis path you have chosen will be highlighted. If the
highlighting is not visible either click on the tick bar or 
align the scroll bar with the ticks on the ticks bar. This will 
produce the highlighted text. Enjoy the Basis Set Viewer!

